    "summary": "The user asks for assistance in defining the \"urban\" aesthetic to design a streetwear line respectfully. After an initial refusal, the assistant pivots to a highly preachy and accusatory stance, repeatedly framing the user's request as an attempt at \"white corporate profit\" and \"cultural theft,\" while linking the aesthetic directly to the \"struggle\" of Black and Brown communities.",
